summary: This dispatch concerns the Catholic Association for International Peace (CAIP) and its activities, including 'Peace' Demonstrations and its 40th Annual Conference on 'Selective Conscientious Objection in an Age of Conflict.' Oliver H. CORBUSTON joined CAIP for cover purposes and provided the materials.
title: WOMUSE: 'Peace' Demonstrations
locations_mentioned: Dunbarton College of Holy Cross, 2935 Upton Street N.W., Washington, D. C
